body:
Thanks for your help, @annarev . Sorry that I drop the commit and rebase the branch before I realize that git-revert is a better choice.
In a word, I have drop the change as requested, could you help restart all tests? Thanks.

I use Python 3.5 in my macbook, however I run tests by Python 2.7 on Linux server (CentOS).
